Host user@ip
    LocalDirectory /absolute/path/to/local/directory
    RemoteDirectory /absolute/path/to/remote/directory
---

------------------------------------------------------
in combination with a ssh config file
------------------------------------------------------
Host HostName
    LocalDirectory /absolute/path/to/local/directory
    RemoteDirectory /absolute/path/to/remote/directory
---

------------------------------------------------------
mount by LocalDirectory
------------------------------------------------------
---
    LocalDirectory /absolute/path/to/local/directory
    RemoteDirectory /absolute/path/to/remote/directory
Host HostName
---

------------------------------------------------------
mount by LocalDirectory and by HostName
------------------------------------------------------
---
    LocalDirectory /absolute/path/to/local/directory
    RemoteDirectory /absolute/path/to/remote/directory
Host HostName
    LocalDirectory /absolute/path/to/second/local/directory
    RemoteDirectory /absolute/path/to/second/remote/directory
---

------------------------------------------------------
mount by HostName and allow PortForwarding
------------------------------------------------------
---
    LocalDirectory /absolute/path/to/local/directory
    RemoteDirectory /absolute/path/to/remote/directory
    PortForwarding yes
Host HostName
---

------------------------------------------------------
mount by LocalDirectory and allow PortForwarding
------------------------------------------------------
Host HostName
    LocalDirectory /absolute/path/to/local/directory
    RemoteDirectory /absolute/path/to/remote/directory
    PortForwarding yes
---
